{"tid":989754,"cid":26,"subCid":0,"title":"(求救)將Point Cloud Data放落BIM 度做Drawing","createTime":"2019-01-21T05:57:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-22T00:56:17.000Z","uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"40d6b689a83f7093d4ac13ade1ef529bd0b4b1f4","tid":989754,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T05:57:18.000Z","msg":"小弟用Faro 3D laser scanner 掃左一間房 <br />\n用左AutoCad Recap(學生版) 整左個Point Cloud 3D view<br />\n如果我想係AutoCad Revit整個3D Model 之後再整埋2D Drawings<br />\n係唔係Export 左個檔 放落revit就可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我上網睇過paper 好似要係Revit整好多Step 先出到圖<br />\n想問下巴打絲打有無教學網可以介紹下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n同埋大約要幾耐時間 會唔會好困難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecd64367e89ee0588c82e85005e83dcf5338d3b7","tid":989754,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:22:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 推"},{"pid":"052180f4e221638471556563f9f0797ee09e9a8a","tid":989754,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T06:42:56.000Z","msg":"推一推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c828b1fcb9f5774dcaebf80a543f4e5b2d278ee0","tid":989754,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:06:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a10e8f3cbbc8cb5216213353f32ee439f383aedd","tid":989754,"uid":190181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:12:00.000Z","msg":"Point Cloud &gt; MeshLab 轉 obj &gt; Revit<br />\n<br />\n利申： 靠估"},{"pid":"9d67d4562d390b8894830b7d6322120514a3cf1e","tid":989754,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score