D再變2D<br />\n始終都要畫返晒element出黎<br />\n先可以由model變返做cad"},{"pid":"476ace4e4c33a2e700bd78055ccc92e096c16ef7","tid":989754,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c348efd3c7af3a690d6288f5fb78364557572f5c","tid":989754,"uid":83799,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"503f7e02daf45ebaa73626a1d900f7b38e0588d3","tid":989754,"uid":92132,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e64422f52595233f73cd8fdb0db72dafba9158ac","tid":989754,"uid":190181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:44:04.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://revitiq.com/point-clouds-revit/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Frevitiq.com%2Fpoint-clouds-revit%2F&d=mfnejbsFhuLinHjNFaGmHP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=8f5bea6a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://revitiq.com/point-clouds-revit/</a><br />\n咁得唔得?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T07:50:17.000Z","msg":"睇左 我就係想知點樣整做實色ELEMENT 好似最後張圖咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-21T16:34:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XAE1gDS.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXAE1gDS.png&h=76a2cc58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上面條link嘅setting<br />\n可以令個point cloud變做彩色<br />\n亦即係條link最後嗰張圖嘅效果<br />\n不過較咗個setting <br />\n個point cloud 都只係一堆彩色點<br />\n<br />\n但要做到你要求<br />\n用point cloud Gen 3D再變2D<br />\n始終都要畫返晒element出黎<br />\n先可以由model變返做cad"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-22T00:56:17.000Z","msg":"唔該哂巴打 我琴日用左一晚摸都畫返D Element出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n原來用Point Cloud做Model係咁煩<br />\n有好多位都係用Recap Pro度Dimension先可以係Revit 度畫出黎<br />\n仲有室內D門 Openings 如果一開始掃唔清楚想畫返出黎都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}